data.description: Located in the desirable Terrace Hills gated community, this updated townhouse features an open floor plan with a modern kitchen featuring painted cabinets and granite counters with bar top, tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and laundry closet. Abundant sunlight and recessed LED lights combined with modern LVP (Luxury Vinyl Plank) flooring create a bright and open feeling in the living areas which flow into the large deck overlooking the greenbelt area. 2 spacious ensuites provide privacy and convenience with their own baths and feature vaulted ceilings and one comes with an additional private balcony. 2 car garage also features an elevated bonus storage/hobby room (perfect man cave/she shed) and driveway for extra parking. Ideally located within this resort-style living community, you are just a short walk to most of the private community amenities which include 2 pools w/spas, club house, basketball court, 2 tennis courts (with pickleball courts coming soon!), RV parking lot, and even a dog park!
